{"tid":1840634,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"笑撚死 春晚特備節目唔係幫武漢打氣 而係不停吹奏黨中央","createTime":"2020-01-25T02:24:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-26T02:35:06.000Z","uid":19552,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"32062f99b22fbc1c64774e3486267844428f58a9","tid":1840634,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T02:24:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />睇完仲嬲呀d支那人 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/eU5mpC4QTTM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FeU5mpC4QTTM&d=EXOoM7fQMXhTNR4rfnaZT4CLuBk19a2msHWYQfvuVO4%3D&h=8b234bb8\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/eU5mpC4QTTM</a>"},{"pid":"5db57e24b04ad60112fadb097ffbe4a679041810","tid":1840634,"uid":9829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T02:24:51.000Z","msg":"咁好嘅文都上唔到熱門<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n[推上去] 罷工比返工救得更多嘅人<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1840117\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1840117</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f27d0766dab672268bbb9b542452f73aeb976af1","tid":1840634,"uid":162008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T02:25:50.000Z","msg":"致四大醫護專業工會<br />\n<br />\n近日致命武漢肺炎肆虐全球，世界各地的政府均已實行嚴謹的防疫措施。唯獨香港特區政府對關口的防疫工作置之不理，令大量懷疑感染新型冠狀病毒的外來患者湧入香港。<br />\n<br />\n港府在防疫工作上力度不足，以及後知後覺的態度，直接令醫護界工作壓力及感染機會大增，甚至需要以抽生死籤來決定進入隔離病房的醫護名單。在未有任何確切治療的方案下，此致命的疫症絕大機會令2003 年沙士事件中，醫護人員因受感染而死亡的傷痛事件重現，再次勾起港人的悲痛回憶。<br />\n<br />\n有見及此，一眾熱心的市民已於2020年1月24日零晨，在《香港地投票》應用程式內發起了一項投票事項。投票只開放予香港境內市民，亦以一系列的措施盡力達至一人一票，其內容如下：<br />\n<br />\n議題：支唔支持醫護大罷工<br />\n投票開放時間：一個月<br />\n截至2020年1月25日零晨為止，24小時內已有1117名香港市民投票，當中約97%支持香港醫護人員罷工，約2%反對及2張廢票。<br />\n<br />\n《香港地投票》應用程式作為一個投票平台，致力為不同民生或政制議題及各種工業行動提供民意基礎。現來信各醫護工會團體，藉此轉達市民的意見。考慮到醫護人員有其專業，亦關乎病人及其家屬的權益。醫護人員罷工與否的決定將完全留待醫護界自行決定，此函只供各大機構作民意參考之用。<br />\n<br />\n香港地投票<br />\n謹啟<br />\n2020-01-25<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hkvote.org/Letter/20200125.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkvote.org%2FLetter%2F20200125.pdf&d=EXOoM7fQMXhTNR4rfnaZT4CLuBk19a2msHWYQfvuVO4%3D&h=ff233059\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hkvote.org/Letter/20200125.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n有勞大家幫我forword 俾醫護工會同各醫護知，唔使有太大道德包袱，因為政府把關不足先係根本問題，呢個民意調查話你地知市民撐你地！會尊重你地既決定"},{"pid":"fb5322706e3b84a2df622b91d402d1b6a4f2e3b1","tid":1840634,"uid":4661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T02:27:23.000Z","msg":"白事當紅事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"207a26c0c89f0a9b07cc9392dc5231dca74e7746","tid":1840634,"uid":321345,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T02:27:39.000Z","msg":"柒味太濃<br />\n睇左10幾秒熄撚左"},{"pid":"33fcc68def49324d15feabba22526b91c15a1344","tid":1840634,"uid":7206,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T02:27:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/On4YxSa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOn4YxSa.jpg&h=105ad711&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"97831aa6e6a06ad28f584f671ba3f37d502a12e6","tid":1840634,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T02:28:39.000Z","msg":"留言功能已停用<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d5f360759b88a35cab58574f71cf7404f6f1448","tid":1840634,"uid":28028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T02:28:41.000Z","msg":"班人講野成個機械人咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c0bba16946c76a4ad7adb7d99aee1f27db17b2e","tid":1840634,"uid":251052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T02:28:45.000Z","msg